47. Uvicorn:
It is light weight web server used to ASGI application like fastapi framework.
i) synchrous request (normal http request)
ii) Asynchrous request(websocket, background task)
WSGI limitation cannot handle webscokets, only support synchrous http request
ASGI solves can handle aynsc + sync support websocket
Webscocket are used when data must update continuously or instanly. communication protocal communicate b/w client and server single long live connection.
Both sides connection are open.
Used for live cricket score, online gaming, food delievery app(swiggy)

