Purpose: It provides tools to build, train, and deploy machine learning and deep learning models across platforms (desktop, mobile, cloud).
Key point: Widely used for tasks like image recognition, NLP, and predictive analytics.


PyTorch and TensorFlow are frameworks (tools) for building AI models.
NLP is a domain of AI focused on language, and it often uses frameworks like PyTorch or TensorFlow to build solutions.

